instruction: Generate a list of characteristics that define a good leader
output:
A good leader has:
- Honesty
- Proactive thinking
- Integrity
- Vision
- Adaptability
- Self-awareness
- Communication Skills 
- Reliability
- Positive Attitude 
- Listening Skills
- Responsibility
- Empathy
- Open-Mindedness
- Trustworthiness 
- Emotional Intelligence
